sql:
SELECT session_id, mode_id, frequency, session_name, description
FROM sessions
WHERE frequency = (SELECT MAX(frequency) FROM sessions);

SELECT sessions.session_name, states.state_name
FROM sessions
INNER JOIN states ON sessions.state_id = states.state_id;

external_knowledge:
- 'Whispered gatherings' metaphorically refers to the names of the public sessions (sessions with `is_private = 0`);
- 'Musical guilds' refers to the bands;
- 'Creators' refers to the full names of the users who created the sessions;
- 'Open forum' implies that the sessions are not private;
- 'Sorted by the name of the gathering and the guild's legacy' indicates the sessions and bands are sorted by their names.

sql:
SELECT session_name 
FROM sessions 
WHERE frequency BETWEEN 40.35 AND 40.45;

SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM sessions 
WHERE created_by IN (SELECT user_id FROM users WHERE is_active = 1);
